videos.description: Louisville's Damion Lee storms into the lane and throws down a dunk for the first points of the game against North Carolina.
videos.headline: Damion Lee starts things off with a bang

videos.description: Louisville's Anas Mahmoud splits the North Carolina defense with a sweet behind-the-back pass to Damion Lee, who finishes at the rim with a layup.
videos.headline: Behind-the-back passes don't get better than this
